-- African Minerals Says It Has Received 167.8 Million Pounds From China
-- Amanda Jordan
-- 2010-06-16T06:07:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-16/african-minerals-says-it-has-received-167-8-million-pounds-from-china.html

          
          
             African Minerals Ltd., which has
iron ore and base metal assets in Sierra Leone, said the
proposed 167.8 million-pound investment by China Railway
Materials Commercial Corp. announced on April 1 has been
completed.  
